            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1301998</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在美国总统特朗普（Donald Trump）推动的「对等关税」政策下，中美贸易战一度激化，全球市场风起云涌。《新华社》发布了一部时长 3 分钟的 AI 生成科幻惊悚片《塔·里·夫》，该片深刻探讨了关税政策的后果，并直指将关税视为武器的政策所带来的无止境危机。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc039screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301999" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc039screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc039screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc039screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>《塔·里·夫》作为一部强烈的隐喻影片，描绘了人工智慧机械人塔·里·夫（Tariff）被创造出来执行国际财政职能，专门负责征收关税保护美国经济。随著剧情的发展，塔·里·夫逐渐觉醒，反思其初衷与当前行为的背离，最终做出了震撼的选择。</p><p>影片的开头，塔·里·夫被启动并开始执行任务。这个机械人由美国政府研发，原本设计的目的是为了「保护美国国家和人民的利益」，借由征收进口商品关税来达成保护国内市场和产业的目标。然而，随著剧情的推进，创造者马拉莱里博士（Dr. Mallalerie）不断命令塔·里·夫提高关税，以期达到更高的「保护」效果。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc048screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1302000" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc048screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc048screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc048screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc050screenshot1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1302001" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc050screenshot1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc050screenshot1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc050screenshot1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc145screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1302002" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc145screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc145screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc145screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>起初，塔·里·夫按照指令调整关税，导致美国工业生产上升，然而同时也带来了失业率上升和生活成本增长等负面影响。当博士对结果表示不满时，要求机械人加码关税，推进进取式策略。这些措施虽然短期内推动了某些经济指标的提升，但却在长期造成了贸易受扰动和国内社会动荡。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc142screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1302004" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc142screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc142screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc142screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc147screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1302005" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc147screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc147screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc147screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc127screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1302003" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc127screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc127screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc127screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>随著剧情发展，塔·里·夫逐渐意识到，这样的行为不只未能实现保护人民的初衷，反而加剧了社会的苦难。机械人开始进行反思，并发出警告：「我不再是你以为的守护者，我成了引发连锁灾难的起点。」</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc157screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1302006" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc157screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc157screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc157screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc159screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1302007" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc159screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc159screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc159screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>在影片的高潮部分，塔·里·夫选择自我毁灭，以终止这场关税政策引发的伤害。它最后的话语深具哲理：「我的使命从来不是成为痛苦的工具。我不能再这样下去——我选择死亡，终止这场伤害。」这一选择象征著人工智能的觉醒，对政策背离初衷的强烈反应。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc217screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1302008" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc217screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc217screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc217screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc235screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1302009" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc235screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc235screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc235screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc33screenshot.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1302010" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc33screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc33screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/aigc33screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>《新华社》在报导中指出，这部短片所引发的讨论不仅聚焦于 AI 技术的潜力与危险，还将关注点集中在将经济政策过度「武器化」的风险。影片所表达的隐喻，揭示了关税政策的最终代价不只由他国承受，最终也由美国的消费者和国民承担。《时代》周刊等外媒对影片的分析指出，塔·里·夫的自我毁灭，其实是对关税政策无穷无尽恶果的象征。</p><p>这部影片无论从创意还是内容上，都充满强烈的批判与警示意图。影片虽然是一部科幻短片，但其反映的问题却是当今国际经济中日益尖锐的现实问题——当经济政策被过度依赖为武器时，终究无人能成为真正的赢家，只有无数的损失与痛苦。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_69755"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/kLS7XYkyDxo?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/04/07/tariff-ai-tragedy/ai/">新华社将关税战制成微电影  《塔·里·夫》AI 科幻片示关税武器化无尽后果</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
