            <title>LG 香港推新窗口式变频冷气，智能冷气及空气洁净产品系列</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/07/lg-air-conditioner/wireless-home/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=lg-air-conditioner</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/07/lg-air-conditioner/wireless-home/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 06:44:07 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[家居无线]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1301895</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>LG 电子今日在香港发布全新智能家居产品系列，重点是搭载最新节能技术及智慧控制的 LG 窗口式变频冷气机，同时展示多款空气洁净产品，包括 LG PuriCare AeroBooster 和双回转变频抽湿机。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7628-scaled.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301909" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7628-694x521.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7628-694x521.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7628-scaled.jpeg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>智慧节能冷气技术，实现全面环保节能</h2><p>发布会重点在于 LG 窗口式变频冷气机，搭载先进 AI 智能节能控制技术，能根据环境变化自动调整制冷强度，确保在炎夏高温下仍能提供舒适凉爽体验。据 LG 技术专家介绍，冷气机具备多档风速调控及智慧温控功能，可减少高达 49% 的能源消耗，特别适合香港地区夏季长期开机使用的需求。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7641-scaled.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301910" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7641-694x521.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7641-694x521.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7641-scaled.jpeg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7636-scaled.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301911" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7636-694x521.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7636-694x521.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7636-scaled.jpeg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7633-scaled.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301912" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7633-694x521.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7633-694x521.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7633-scaled.jpeg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>冷气机亦兼顾环保考量，采用符合国际标准的 R32 冷媒，减少对臭氧层的破坏，同时优化能效比（EER），在节能与性能之间达到最佳平衡。与此同时，产品内建的智能空气流动系统，可将冷气均匀分布至房间各个角落，避免冷风直吹人体，增强整体舒适度。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7637-scaled.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301913" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7637-694x521.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7637-694x521.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7637-scaled.jpeg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>智能空气管理，多元化应用选择</h2><p>为了满足不同家庭和空间的需求，LG 窗口式变频冷气机共推出 5 种型号，从 0.75 匹到 2.5 匹不等，涵盖单身公寓至大型客厅的应用场景。特别是在睡眠模式下，冷气机会自动降低运行音量，并透过智慧控温功能维持凉爽而安静的环境。</p><p>冷气机内建远程控制功能，透过 LG ThinQ 应用程式，使用者可以随时掌控设备运行状态及温度设置，特别是在外出时提前启动或关闭冷气，大大提升操作便利性。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7608-scaled.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301901" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7608-694x521.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7608-694x521.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7608-scaled.jpeg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2></h2><h2>空气洁净产品同步亮相  创造清新健康空间</h2><p>除冷气机外，LG 亦展示了多款空气净化产品，包括 LG PuriCare AeroBooster 智能空气清新机和双回转变频抽湿机，这些设备能有效清除空气中的悬浮微粒及异味，特别适合空气质素堪忧的都市环境。</p><p>LG PuriCare AeroBooster 采用 360 度环绕送风系统，内建 HEPA 过滤及活性炭除臭滤网，能去除 99.9% 的过敏原及 PM2.5 微粒。特有的 Pet Mode 专为饲养宠物的家庭设计，能有效去除毛发及异味，提升空气洁净度。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7645-scaled.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301920" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7645-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7645-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7645-scaled.jpeg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/d25b699b804a44878967.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301900" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/d25b699b804a44878967-580x580.jpeg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/d25b699b804a44878967-580x580.jpeg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/d25b699b804a44878967.jpeg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/d25b699b804a44878967-144x144.jpeg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p>在抽湿方面，LG 双回转变频抽湿机，配备高效智能湿度控制，可自动感应环境湿度并动态调节除湿力度。内建抗菌滤网，确保在保持干燥同时，有效阻隔霉菌及尘螨滋生，适合在潮湿多雨的季节使用。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7644-scaled.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301915" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7644-694x521.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7644-694x521.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7644-scaled.jpeg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7643-scaled.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301916" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7643-694x521.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7643-694x521.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7643-scaled.jpeg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7642-scaled.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301917" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7642-493x580.jpeg" alt="" width="493" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7642-493x580.jpeg 493w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_7642-scaled.jpeg 765w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 493px" /></a></p><p>LG 产品策略聚焦于整合冷气及空气管理技术，全面提升室内环境品质。</p><p>LG 表示，未来公司将继续推动家电智能化升级，透过引入更多 AI 技术，让智慧家庭不只节能，更能有效应对现代都市空气污染问题。</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/04/07/lg-air-conditioner/wireless-home/">LG 香港推新窗口式变频冷气，智能冷气及空气洁净产品系列</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
